headline: 5 Financial Transaction Stocks in Focus Amid Strong Cross-Border Volumes

headline: Is Mastercard Still a Smart Pick After $250 Million Strategic Investment in Egypt?
summary: If you have been keeping an eye on Mastercard lately, you are not alone. Investors everywhere are weighing whether now is the right moment to buy, hold, or sell this payments powerhouse. Over the last twelve months, Mastercard stock has racked up a healthy 23.6% increase, and so far this year, the momentum has continued with a 13.1% gain. Even a slight dip of 0.2% in the past week has not dimmed the optimism fueled by recent industry developments, such as ongoing digital payment innovation...
